property_details:
Rising gracefully from a premier waterfront property in downtown Sarasota, The Ritz-Carlton Residences, Sarasota Bay invites residents into a world designed to delight. Set along The Quay and surrounded by a vibrant metropolis, it opens the door to refined culture and cuisine, the finest shopping, and exceptional entertainment. Inside the tower, and throughout beautifully landscaped outdoor amenity spaces, residents enjoy an oasis of privacy where legendary service and personalized attention elevate every detail of life in the heart of the Cultural Capital of Florida., 
Each elegant residence in the limited collection at The Ritz-Carlton Residences, Sarasota Bay is thoughtfully designed to serve as the ideal stage for the unique lifestyle residents wish to create. Dramatic, large-scale windows envelop residents in luminous panoramic views while bathing interiors in natural light. Spacious, exquisitely finished floor plans open to expansive private terraces that are perfect for morning tea, festive al fresco dining delivered from downstairs, or simply relaxing in the balmy tropical climate.
amenity_details:
A sophisticated Formal Social Room for private gatherings or entertaining
A spectacular elevated waterfront amenity terrace showcases sweeping harbor views and features a resort-style pool with an integrated sun shelf, a spa, open gathering spaces and intimate conversation areas
Dog Park and Pet Washing Station
Waterfront News Café with daily coffee/beverage station and comfortable seating areas to catch up on daily news or enjoy the game on large screen TVs
Board Room for private or group meetings
These exceptional amenities and resort-style pleasures are complemented by an impressive Food and Beverage program, serviced by an exclusive, on-site kitchen, offering:
Morning coffee shop featuring a diverse range of coffee choices and a selection of convenient grab-and-go breakfast items
Lunch and dinner menus feature made-to-order items including fresh salads and sandwiches, healthy bowls, and artisan cheese boards. The menu will be extended with dinner options
Bar menu features a variety of adult beverage options, including beer, wine, spirits, and frozen drinks
One touch, App-based service enables effortless ordering for pick up or delivery to residences and amenity areas
developer_details: Headquartered in Palm Beach County, Florida, Kolter has introduced a vision for luxury that is continually raising expectations for homebuyers and establishing new standards for the industry. Committed to “Creating Better Communities,” The company brings over twenty years of innovative residential development to each new endeavor. The Kolter Group recognizes that with each new home sale, there is an inherent commitment to deliver not just a quality residence, but a unique, amenity-rich lifestyle. With that in mind, the company strives to deliver the most sought-after, energy-efficient designs, complete with the best finishes and amenities. Kolter has developed over $10 billion of residential projects (both completed and in process) including a number of exceptional condominium residences in water-front, water-view and amenity-rich walkable urban locations.
architect_details: Over the past 50 years, SB Architects has established a world-wide reputation for excellence and leadership in the planning and design of large-scale hotels, resorts, destination resort communities, and all associated resort amenities, as well as large-scale multifamily residential and urban mixed-use projects. A mid-size firm by design, the dedicated staff in their San Francisco and Miami offices successfully merges unmatched experience with the energy, drive and dedication of a second generation of partners. SB Architects are global and hands-on, industry leading team players, passionate and pragmatic, highly professional and relationship driven.
builder_details: Moss Construction is a national privately held construction firm providing innovative solutions resulting in award-winning projects. With regional offices across the United States, Moss focuses on construction management, solar EPC, and design-build. The company’s diverse portfolio encompasses a wide range of sectors, including luxury high-rise residential, landmark mixed-use developments, hospitality, K-12 and higher education, justice, solar energy and battery storage, and sports. Moss is ranked by Engineering News-Record as the nation’s top solar contractor and one of the top 50 general contractors. Moss prides itself on a strong entrepreneurial culture that honors safety, quality, client engagement, and employee development. Its employees consistently rank Moss as one of the best places to work.
